## ‚ñ∂Ô∏è Getting Started

### 1. Clone the repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/edxcellence-crm.git
````

---

## üñ• Frontend Setup

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

Create `.env`:

```
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000
```

---

## üõ° Backend Setup

```bash
cd backend
npm install
npm start
```

Create `.env`:

```
MONGO_URL=YOUR_MONGO_DB_URL
JWT_SECRET=EDXCELLENCE_SECRET_123
PORT=5000
```

---

## üîå API Endpoints (Core)

### Auth

| Method | Endpoint      | Description       |
| ------ | ------------- | ----------------- |
| POST   | `/auth/login` | Login user        |
| GET    | `/auth/me`    | Current user info |

---

### Users

| Method | Endpoint     | Description      |
| ------ | ------------ | ---------------- |
| GET    | `/users`     | Fetch all users  |
| POST   | `/users`     | Create user      |
| PUT    | `/users/:id` | Update user      |
| DELETE | `/users/:id` | Soft delete user |

---

### Roles

| Method | Endpoint     | Description     |
| ------ | ------------ | --------------- |
| GET    | `/roles`     | Get all roles   |
| POST   | `/roles`     | Create new role |
| PUT    | `/roles/:id` | Update role     |

---

### Leads

| Method | Endpoint | Description   |
| ------ | -------- | ------------- |
| GET    | `/leads` | Get all leads |
| POST   | `/leads` | Add lead      |

---

### Deals

| Method | Endpoint     | Description |
| ------ | ------------ | ----------- |
| GET    | `/deals`     | Get deals   |
| POST   | `/deals`     | Add deal    |
| PUT    | `/deals/:id` | Update deal |

---

### Activity Log

| Method | Endpoint         | Description |
| ------ | ---------------- | ----------- |
| GET    | `/activity/logs` | Fetch logs  |

---

## üîê RBAC Matrix

| Module      | SuperAdmin | Admin | Manager | Staff   |
| ----------- | ---------- | ----- | ------- | ------- |
| Users       | FULL       | EDIT  | VIEW    | NONE    |
| Roles       | FULL       | EDIT  | VIEW    | NONE    |
| Leads       | FULL       | FULL  | FULL    | LIMITED |
| Deals       | FULL       | FULL  | FULL    | LIMITED |
| System Logs | FULL       | VIEW  | NONE    | NONE    |

---

## üåì Theme (Light / Dark Mode)

Toggle is stored in:

```
localStorage.theme
```

Colors adjust using Tailwind classes + CSS variables.

