## üöÄ Deployment

### Frontend (Vercel)

```bash
npm run build
vercel deploy
```

### Backend (Render)

* Create new Web Service
* Add environment variables
* Deploy from GitHub
* Auto deploy on push

### MongoDB Atlas

* Create shared cluster
* Allow IP 0.0.0.0/0 (dev)
* Add connection string to backend `.env`

